      "message": "fix: stabilize Clerk token getter to prevent session flashing\n\ngetToken from useAuth() changes reference on every Clerk session tick,\ncausing infinite re-renders via useCallback dependency chain. Store it\nin a ref so the tokenGetter callback identity stays stable.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
